### Health check
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health

### List documents
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/documents/list

### Get one document
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/documents/YOUR_DOCUMENT_ID_HERE

### Query knowledge base
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/chat/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "这个文档主要讲了什么？",
  "top_k": 3
}

### Chat history
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/chat/history?limit=10

### Rebuild one document
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/documents/YOUR_DOCUMENT_ID_HERE/rebuild

### Rebuild all documents
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/documents/rebuild-all

### Delete one document
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/documents/YOUR_DOCUMENT_ID_HERE
